			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For the history of Earth which includes the time before human existence, see <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Earth" title="History of the Earth">History of the Earth</a>. For the field of historical study that examines history from a global perspective, see <a href="/wiki/World_History" title="World History">World History</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_world_(disambiguation)" title="History of the world (disambiguation)">History of the world (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Recorded_history" title="Recorded history">recorded history</a>.</div>
